    "message_2": "To solve the given first-order ordinary differential equation (ODE) using the fourth-order Runge-Kutta method, we will follow these steps:\n\n1. Define the ODE function: y' = f(t, y) = -0.5y + 3\n2. Set the initial conditions: t0 = 0, y0 = 1, and step size h = 0.2\n3. Apply the fourth-order Runge-Kutta method to find the approximate values of y at t = 0.2, t = 0.4, t = 0.6, and t = 0.8.\n\nThe fourth-order Runge-Kutta method is given by:\n\nk1 = h * f(t, y)\nk2 = h * f(t + h/2, y + k1/2)\nk3 = h * f(t + h/2, y + k2/2)\nk4 = h * f(t + h, y + k3)\ny_new = y + (k1 + 2*k2 + 2*k3 + k4) / 6\n\nNow, we will apply the method for each time step:\n\nt = 0.2:\nk1 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * 1 + 3) = 0.4\nk2 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1 + 0.4/2) + 3) = 0.39\nk3 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1 + 0.39/2) + 3) = 0.3805\nk4 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1 + 0.3805) + 3) = 0.361975\ny1 = 1 + (0.4 + 2*0.39 + 2*0.3805 + 0.361975) / 6 = 1.390825\n\nt = 0.4:\nk1 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * 1.390825 + 3) = 0.3046625\nk2 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.390825 + 0.3046625/2) + 3) = 0.298546375\nk3 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.390825 + 0.298546375/2) + 3) = 0.29726754375\nk4 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.390825 + 0.29726754375) + 3) = 0.290074846875\ny2 = 1.390825 + (0.3046625 + 2*0.298546375 + 2*0.29726754375 + 0.290074846875) / 6 = 1.68526754375\n\nt = 0.6:\nk1 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * 1.68526754375 + 3) = 0.214366228125\nk2 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.68526754375 + 0.214366228125/2) + 3) = 0.21017911484375\nk3 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.68526754375 + 0.21017911484375/2) + 3) = 0.209589557421875\nk4 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.68526754375 + 0.209589557421875) + 3) = 0.205402444140625\ny3 = 1.68526754375 + (0.214366228125 + 2*0.21017911484375 + 2*0.209589557421875 + 0.205402444140625) / 6 = 1.895589557421875\n\nt = 0.8:\nk1 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * 1.895589557421875 + 3) = 0.1522052212890625\nk2 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.895589557421875 + 0.1522052212890625/2) + 3) = 0.14900911064453125\nk3 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.895589557421875 + 0.14900911064453125/2) + 3) = 0.14850955532226562\nk4 = 0.2 * (-0.5 * (1.895589557421875 + 0.14850955532226562) + 3) = 0.14531344467773437\ny4 = 1.895589557421875 + (0.1522052212890625 + 2*0.14900911064453125 + 2*0.14850955532226562 + 0.14531344467773437) / 6 = 2.0485095553222656\n\nSo, the approximate values of y are:\ny(0.2) ≈ 1.390825\ny(0.4) ≈ 1.68526754375\ny(0.6) ≈ 1.895589557421875\ny(0.8) ≈ 2.0485095553222656"
